00:00:30.949 --> 00:00:32.700
Can I ask you one more question?

00:00:35.119 --> 00:00:36.704
Were there any women?

00:00:37.664 --> 00:00:39.415
- Yes.
- Really?

00:00:39.582 --> 00:00:41.292
Yes.

00:00:41.543 --> 00:00:44.295
- What was that like?
