00:00:54.806 --> 00:00:57.141
Made me sit on her lap
and do things? Yeah.

00:00:58.768 --> 00:01:02.230
- What? You sat on her lap?
- Mm-hm.

00:01:02.397 --> 00:01:05.191
- She told you what to do?
- Mm-hm.

00:01:05.358 --> 00:01:10.488
Oh, my God. Nikki hated when I talked
